                            <comment id="14475507" author="jimwhite" created="Wed, 26 Feb 2014 03:36:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;While handling URLs in the classpath is not really worthwhile for pre-2.3.0 Groovy, I think eliminating the use of URL.equals should probably be done for earlier versions as a bug fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14475530" author="jimwhite" created="Wed, 26 Feb 2014 03:38:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch added to PR #337.  This almost deserves it&apos;s own pull, but my codebase and the test code currently rely on the other stuff in #337.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14480457" author="paulk" created="Sun, 6 Apr 2014 01:21:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So Jim, was this resolved with PR#337 or is their more work to do? From the description above and the code in the PR, I think we are all good - just double checking with you.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
